<p>SCP Containment need.<br />
Need, need, needs to feed.<br />
So take my words and heed&#8230; HEED!<br />
That two-six-seven-three cannot be freed!</p>
<p>Free&#8230; FREE&#8230; Free your mind!<br />
This skip cannot infect our kind<br />
Just as long as it will find<br />
Another word that can be rhymed!</p>
<p>HEED! Not FREE!<br />
FIND! That which RHYMED in your MIND!<br />
For&#8230; our&#8230;<br />
kind.</p>
